P(C^+|(t1^+ \text{ or } t2^+)
P(t1^+  \text{ or }  t2^+|C^+) P(C^+)\over P(t1^+  \text{ or }  t2^+).
P(t1^+  \text{ or }  t2^+|C^+) = P(t1^+|C^+)+P(t2^+|C^+)-P(t1^+  \text{ and }  t2^+|C^+)?
P(t2^+|t1^+) ={ P(t1^+ \text{ and } t2^+)\over P(t1^+)}?
